\cf3\i     [kicker: \u8961? III.06 \u183? An old idea, again]\i0\cf0\par
    \u171? Empty cups are easier to fill. \u187?\par
\par
    A Zen teacher pours tea for a busy student until the cup overflows. The student says: master, the cup is full . The teacher says: so are you . Bada Shanren's fish, like an empty cup, is mostly absence. \u8961? Bada Shanren \u183? Fish \u183? c. 1690.\par
