\par\par\cf2\b\f2\fs32 \u9619?\u9619?\u9619? 47 VI-ARDEN DAILY\b0\f0\fs28\cf0\par
\cf3\i     [punch lines \u8212? let the line break do the timing]\i0\cf0\par
\par
\cf3\i     [kicker: \u8961? VI.03 \u183? Hokusai's confession]\i0\cf0\par
    \u171? At seventy-three I began to understand animals. \u187?\par
\par
    Hokusai wrote, in his old age: at six I drew. At fifty I had published much. At seventy I had nothing worth keeping. At seventy-three I began to understand the structure of birds and beasts. Maybe by ninety, he said, I will be alive. He died at eighty-eight. Still on the way. \u8961? Two Cranes \u183? LACMA \u183? PD.\par
