\cf3\i     [kicker: \u8961? IX.04 \u183? A small case]\i0\cf0\par
    \u171? Cooking dinner is the cheapest religion I know. \u187?\par
\par
    My mother taught me to make rice by smelling the steam. There is a moment, just before the rice is done, when the smell turns from grass to bread. You cannot set a timer for it. You learn it once and you have it forever, like a prayer. \u8961? Hiroshige \u183? Plum Park \u183? 1857.\par
